Description: African Red Slip Ware wheel-made pottery vessel sherd. Orange-red fabric.
Curator's comments: African Red Slip red slip tableware sherd. Base similar to ARS form 91C-D base (Hayes 1972, 140-4) Hayes, J.W. 1972. Late Roman Pottery. London.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (IF.092) (Phase 3)
